About
Discover
Our Story
Deeply rooted in the Orlando community, Bounce House is a place where individuals come together to celebrate the memories they’ve made over the years.
Boasting a large variety of refined cocktails and delectable eats, we know we will satisfy your craving for quality.
Treat yourself to some of the best cuisine and customer service in Orlando and come eat, drink and BOUNCE with us!
What Bounce House
Is All About
